	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Okay...<BR>
1: This spell will NOT stack with Breeze.  I've tried it.<BR>
2: I don't know what you guys are thinking, but this spell is just waaay to slow to be used during combat and have it actually be helpful in regaining mana.<BR>
3: You don't lose HP when you use this spell...you just don't gain any...i.e. if you have three bubbles of life and You cast Dark Pact your life will remain at three bubbles while your mana shoots up at double the normal rate until the spell wears off.<BR>
4: This spell just plain rocks.  I'm on level 13 and just started using it...up until now I've had to go around begging Enchanters for Breeze and Clarity and put up with that holier than thou attitude they always seem to get when you ask them.  If you use this spell after each battle, I guarantee you'll have waaay less downtime and much more fun because you'll be playing that much more.  <BR>
**Fadaar**<BR>
13th Level Necromancer<BR>
Mith Marr
				</font>
